<html>

<head>
<title>Incredibly Simple Shopping</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="pb-2 mt-4 mb-2 border-bottom">
	<h1><%=items.name%></h1>
	<p>(<a href="/items">back</a>)</p>
</div>

<div class="row"> 	
	<div class="col-4">
		<img class="img-fluid" src="%=items.img_url%">
	</div>

	<div class="col-4">
		<div>Occasionally rabid, but always there for you.</div>
		<div><em>$<%=items.price%></em></div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="row my-4">
	<div class="col-8">
		<h3>Reviews</h3>
		<div class="card w-100 mt-3">
			<div class="card-body">
				<%if (locals.error) { %>
					<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
						A simple danger alertâ€”check it out!
						<%=error%>
					  </div>
				<% } %>

				<form action="/item_view_response/:items.id" method="POST">
					<div class="form-group">
						<label>Add your review!</label>
					 	<input class="form-control mb-1" placeholder="Name"/>
					 </div>
					 <div class="form-group">
						<textarea class="form-control mb-1" placeholder="Review"></textarea>
					 </div>
					<div class="form-group">
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
					</div>
				</form>

			</div>
		</div>

		<% for (let [i, item] of items.entries()) { %>
			<div class="card w-100 mt-3">
				<div class="card-header" href="/item_view/<%=i%>">
					<em><%=item.author%></em>
				</div>

				<div class="card-body">
					<p>I get a new one of these every week! They're great.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		<% } %>

		<div class="card w-100 mt-3">
			<div class="card-header">
				<em>horace</em>
			</div>

			<div class="card-body">
				<p>HELP! They're chewing through thhshshssseasv nevr mnd u go away al gud her yum yum yum</p>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>

</html>
